quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  37,139,Soni chisimu Yunusu jwaliji mwa Achimitenga
  37,140,(Kumbuchilani) ndema ja jwatilile m’chombo chepachile
  37,141,"Basi ni ŵatesile ndoto (kuti ŵatijagwile ndotojo aponyedwe m’mesi), basi ni jwaliji (Yunusu) mwa akwagwila (ndoto)"
  37,142,Basi ni chammisile chinsomba aku juli jwagambidwa
  37,143,Basi ingaŵa kuti jwalakwe jwaliji mwa akunswejesya (Allah)
  37,144,Chisimu jungatemi m’matumbo mwakwe kwikanila lisiku lyakuwukulidwa (ŵandu m’malembe)
  37,145,Basi twamponyisye munjengwe jambembembe juli jwakulwala
  37,146,Ni twammechesye chitela cha mongumbondu (mbonda syekulungwa syati mpela mongu)
  37,147,"Ni twantumisye ku (ŵandu) masausande gakwana lichila (,000) nambo soni ŵakupunda pele"
  37,148,"Ni ŵakulupilile, basi ni twasengwasyisye kwikanila ndema (jao jakuwila)"
  37,149,"Basi mwawusyani (achimakafili ŵa pa Maaka mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ kuti): “Ana Ambuje ŵenu ni akwete ŵanache ŵachikongwe, sano ŵanganyao ni akwete ŵanache ŵachilume?”"
  37,150,“Kapena twagumbile Achimalaika kuŵa achakongwe aku ŵanganyao achitendelaga umboni?”
  37,151,"Manyililani yanti, ŵanganyao ni unami ŵao akuŵechetaga yanti"
  37,152,“Allah aŵeleche (ŵanache ŵachikongwe ŵali Achimalaika).” Soni chisimu ŵanganyao ŵaunami kusyene
  37,153,Ana (Allah) jusagwile ŵanache ŵachikongwe kwaleka ŵachilume
  37,154,"Chipali chichi kukwenu, ana nkulamula chinauli"
  37,155,Ana ngankukumbuchila (yanti Allah juŵambalene nayo yakola mwanache)
  37,156,Kapena jenumanja nkwete umboni wakuonechela (wa yankuŵechetayi)
  37,157,Basi ikani nacho chitabu chenu nam’baga jenumanja nkuŵecheta yakuona
  37,158,Ni asepelele ŵanganyao ulongo chilikati cha Jwalakwe (Allah) ni majini. Nambo majini ni gamanyiliile kusyene yanti chisimu ŵanganyao (achimakafilio) tachija kuonechela (kwa Allah kuti akajiilanye magambo ga unami wao)
  37,159,Allah aŵambalene nayo kusyene yaakusimba ŵanganyao
  37,160,Ikaŵeje achikapolo ŵa Allah ŵakuswejesyedwa (ŵanganyao ni ŵaakunswejesya Allah ku yaakunnambuchisya achimakafili)
  37,161,Sano chisimu jenumanja (achimakafili) ni yankuigalagatila (isanamu)
  37,162,Nganim’ba jenumanja ŵanti ni kunsochelesyanayo (jwalijose mu ŵakulupilila kuti anneche Allah)
  37,163,Ikaŵeje ajula jwatakajinjile ku Moto Waukali
  37,164,Soni pangali jwalijose mwetuwe (Achimalaika) ikaŵeje jukwete malo gakumanyika (kwinani gakutendela ibada)
  37,165,Soni chisimu uwwe (Achimalaika) tukwimaga m’misela (pakuswali)
  37,166,Soni chisimu uwwe (Achimalaika) tukunswejesyaga (Allah pa kuswali)
  37,167,Soni chisimu ŵanganyaŵa (achimakafili ŵacharabu) ŵatiji
  37,168,"“Ingaŵe twakwete uwwe chikumbusyo muŵakolele ŵandu ŵandanda,”"
  37,169,“Chisimu tungaliji achikapolo ŵa Allah ŵakuswejesyedwa.”
  37,170,"Basi (pachaichilile chikumbusyo) ŵachikanile, basi tachiyika kumanyilila (yatinjatenda)"
  37,171,Soni chisimu chene pamasile pa lyalongolele liloŵe Lyetu kwa achikapolo Ŵetu Achimitenga
  37,172,(Lyanti) chisimu ŵanganyao ni ŵatakamuchisyidwe
  37,173,Nambo soni kuti asilikali Ŵetu chisimu ni ŵataŵe ŵakupunda
  37,174,Basi mwatundumalilani kwa kandaŵi kannono
  37,175,Soni gambagani kwalola; basi sampano taione
  37,176,Ana akuijanguya ilagasyo Yetu
  37,177,"Basi (ilagasyo) patiichituluchila paluŵala pao (tachijonanjidwa), ni kuchiŵa kundaŵi kwakusakala nnope kwa akuteteledwa"
  37,178,Soni mwatundumalilani kwa kandaŵi kannono
  37,179,Soni gambagani kwalola; basi sampano taione
  37,180,"Aŵambalene kusyene Ambuje ŵenu (Allah), Ambuje ŵamachili gakupunda ku yaakwasimba nayo (achimakafili)"
  37,181,Soni ntendele uŵe kwa Achimitenga
  37,182,Soni lumbili losope lwene alapikwe Allah M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope